{"blocks":[{"key":"3gf3m","text":"On the clean bench, take 50 mg of scented glands and put them into a pre-cooled mortar to ensure that the liquid nitrogen has never passed the sample, quickly grind the sample into powder, add 1 ml TRIZOL, mix the tissue powder with TRIZOL, and put it into In a centrifuge tube, stand at room temperature for 15 min.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"ea063","text":"    ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1},{"key":1,"offset":2,"length":1}],"data":[]},{"key":"9ekob","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"E09FBDC0A29711ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":"51373","label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"","unit":32}},"1":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":900,"guid":"25B67050A29A11ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":"82502","label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"34sm7","text":"Add the mixed solution to the purification column, centrifuge at 12000r/min at 4°C for 2 min, repeat three times to ensure that ethanol is removed.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"3fndm","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":[]},{"key":"27d95","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"shaker","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":120,"error_shaker":false,"error_temperature":false,"guid":"CACDF800A29B11ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"scientificNotation":{"shaker":false,"temperature":false},"shaker":"12000","start":null,"temperature":"4","temperatureUnit":10,"unit":33}}}}
